  "version": 1,
  "_doc": "Canonical merchant-string -> supplier+ticker map for the Shovel Intelligence engine. Loaded at boot by DiscoveryService and served read-only by GET /supplier-map. Rules are evaluated in declaration order; first match wins. Authors: put MORE-SPECIFIC tokens BEFORE less-specific ones (e.g. 'AMZN MKTPLACE' before 'AMAZON'). 'match' is upper-cased on load — write it however; matching is case-insensitive.",
